title: Received Riot Kayle, but not icon
body: I received Riot Kayle, but have not received the icon.

replies.body: We're still in the process of sending out gifts per our current [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight until this is all wrapped up.  The gifts will come!
